{{Infobox musical artist |image = AsiehAhmadi.jpg |image_size = |background = non_vocal_instrumentalist |birth_date = {{birth year and age|1983}} |origin = [[Tehran]], [[Iran]] |instrument = [[Tanbur]], [[Dayereh]], [[Daf]] |genre = [[Persian traditional music]] |occupation = [[Composer]] |years_active = 2000–present }}
'''Asieh Ahmadi''' ({{lang-fa|آسیه احمدی}}) (born 5 June 1983 in [[Tehran]]) is an [[Iranian peoples|Iranian]] [[daf]], [[dayereh]] and [[tanbur]] player.<ref>[http://spanish.irib.ir/radioculture/artes/m%C3%BAsica/item/168502-conjunto-persa-realizar%C3%A1-conciertos-en-turqu%C3%ADa Conjunto persa realizará conciertos en Turquía]</ref><ref>[http://www.asremardom.com/post/19008/%D8%B5%D9%81%D8%AD%D9%87-12-9-%D9%85%D8%B1%D8%AF%D8%A7%D8%AF-92 تنبورنوازی «حنانه» در کنار مزار مولانا] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141204193526/http://www.asremardom.com/post/19008/%D8%B5%D9%81%D8%AD%D9%87-12-9-%D9%85%D8%B1%D8%AF%D8%A7%D8%AF-92 |date=December 4, 2014 }}</ref><ref>[http://cinemayeno.com/index.aspx?siteid=1&pageid=140&newsview=17678 گروه موسیقی " حنانه " در تالار رودکی برای کرمانشاه می‌نوازد]</ref><ref>[http://www.presstv.ir/detail/2013/07/31/316503/iran-ensemble-holds-concert-in-turkey/ Iran Hannaneh music ensemble performs concert in Konya] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131206053431/http://www.presstv.ir/detail/2013/07/31/316503/iran-ensemble-holds-concert-in-turkey/ |date=December 6, 2013 }}</ref> She is the sister of [[Sara Ahmadi]]. Ahmadi has made numerous recordings with prominent musicians including [[Abdolhossein Mokhtabad]], [[Nasser Razazi]], [[Pari Zanganeh]] and [[Simin Ghanem]], and is a member of the Musical groups [[Hannaneh group|Hannaneh]] and [[Toranj group|Toranj]].<ref>[http://www.tabnak.ir/fa/mobile/news/335759/هم‌نوا-با-تار-کیوان-ساکت-شوید-فیلم بازگشت سنتی‌خوان‌ها روی صحنه؛ از سالار عقیلی تا وحید تاج]{{dead link|date=October 2016 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>[https://archive.is/20141130080448/http://www.yjc.ir/fa/news/4451418/%D8%B4%D8%A8-%D9%85%D9%88%D8%B3%DB%8C%D9%82%DB%8C-%DA%A9%D8%B1%D9%85%D8%A7%D9%86%D8%B4%D8%A7%D9%87-%D8%AF%D8%B1-%D8%AA%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%B1-%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%AF%DA%A9%DB%8C شب موسیقی کرمانشاه در تالار رودکی]</ref><ref>[http://www.musicema.com/node/175041 کنسرت گروه موسی